      "description": "Presenting a peerless example of automotive excellence, this vehicle is offered in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. Meticulously preserved and maintained to an exacting standard, it represents the definitive pinnacle of its class. Every aesthetic detail and mechanical assembly reflects a level of care that satisfies the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of unrivaled integrity and aesthetic perfection.",
      "price": 44800.0,
